<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Registrasi Berhasil</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .success-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
      }
      .success-icon {
        color: #4caf50;
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .note-section {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }
      .note-section ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
      }
      .note-section li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .note-section li:before {
        content: "\F633";
        font-family: "bootstrap-icons";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #4caf50;
      }
      .btn-back {
        transition: transform 0.2s;
      }
      .btn-back:hover {
        transform: translateX(-5px);
      }
      .whatsapp-link {
        color: #25d366;
        text-decoration: none;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .whatsapp-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="success-card">
        <div class="text-center">
          <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill success-icon"></i>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Registrasi Berhasil!</h2>
          <p class="lead mb-4">
            Terima kasih telah mendaftar! Data anda sudah kami rekam. Cek email
            anda untuk memperoleh QR Code yang bisa digunakan saat pendaftaran
            ulang.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="note-section">
          <h5 class="mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>Catatan Penting:
          </h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Jangan lupa untuk registrasi ulang setiap harinya pada jadwal yang
              sudah ditentukan
            </li>
            <li>
              Jika berhalangan hadir, segera batalkan reservasi melalui web ini
              (link tutorial pembatalan tertera di email)
            </li>
            <li>
              Silahkan masuk ke grup berikut agar tidak tertinggal informasi
              berkaitan dengan itikaf
              <br /><a
                class="whatsapp-link"
                href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/FRSsgWWhBMwDnk0Cj31i4B"
              >
                <i class="bi bi-whatsapp me-1"></i
                >https://chat.whatsapp.com/FRSsgWWhBMwDnk0Cj31i4B
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/itikaf" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-back">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>Kembali ke Halaman Utama
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
